definitions.definition: The ninth month of the Gregorian calendar , following August and preceding October , containing the southward equinox .
examples: Late September is a beautiful time of year.
This was one of the warmest Septembers on record.

definitions.definition: A female or male given name transferred from the month name [in turn from English] .

main_definition: The ninth month of the Gregorian calendar , following August and preceding October , containing the southward equinox .
